OL,4,CEx-Brewdog staff allege culture of fear
OL,5,Cat brewer
OL,6, Former staff at Brewdog have alleged a
OL,7, "culture of fear" at the beer firm with
OL,8, a "toxic attitude" to junior employees.
OL,10,FIn an open letter, signatories said a
OL,11,F"significant number" of former staff
OL,12,Fhad "suffered mental illness as a
OL,13,Fresult of working at BrewDog".
OL,15,FThey claimed that the firm was built
OL,16,Faround a "cult of personality" of
OL,17,Ffounders James Watt and Martin Dickie.
OL,19,FMr Watt said Brewdog was "sorry" and
OL,20,Fthat it would not contest the letter,
OL,21,Fbut "listen, learn and act".
